{"tid":2419330,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［僭建］其實屋宇署係咪真係會做嘢？","createTime":"2021-02-23T08:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T11:31:55.000Z","uid":2127,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"339ef7716367da10280f03e6636cba7e5973c86b","tid":2419330,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyi7xOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffyi7xOt.png&h=195890e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7V3Wq8u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7V3Wq8u.png&h=15b785d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49M5jtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49M5jtw.png&h=205b5f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前send咗email去舉報，啱啱收到回覆👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>又一村玉寶閣1A及1B單位的僭建問題</strong><br />\n<br />\n先生/女士，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本署派員到上址視察，發現1樓A室、B室外牆及其地下花園有僭建物，按照現行對僭建<br />\n物的執法政策，本署已向有關業主發出清拆令，著令其清拆有關僭建物。本署會繼續<br />\n緊密跟進有關清拆令的遵辦情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪真係會拆呢，唔拆又點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d899fcade9a7f48344bb2621c2c83a8d0c67eedd","tid":2419330,"uid":56624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"清拆令可以唔拆住，拖到好撚叻死死果日都唔使拆（不過要罰錢）<br />\n<br />\n呢單2007年去到2020年都未拆<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202006/23/P2020062300256.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202006%2F23%2FP2020062300256.htm&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv38kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=519aa8aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202006/23/P2020062300256.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f72a31210b791990f30fb9debf2c9a27a6a7e7d","tid":2419330,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d899fcade9a7f48344bb2621c2c83a8d0c67eedd","tid":2419330,"uid":56624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy"